>                                         PART 2: Prepare globals and define paths
>                                         PART 3: Set codebook template
>                                         PART 4: Correct variable types
>                                         PART 5: Variable creation
>                                         PART 6: Outcome indicators
>                                         PART 7: Label variables
>                                         PART 8: Save dataset for analysis
>                                 
>         ** REQUIRES:    ${c -(}dataset{c )-}/Somalia Cost of inaction dataset June 2023_10 July 2023.dta
